Application Components Debuggable

Summary : It was found that some applications were using components with debug=true flag enabled.

OWASP Category: M3: 2016 Insecure Communication

Severity :   Low  

Complexity : Easy 

From : Remote / External

Steps to Reproduce:

Proof of Concept : Attached in the Video


Impact : An Adversary can access sensitive data if debugging is enabled.

Affected Path: Entire Application

Recommendations : Applications should disable debugging.
 
References : 
https://resources.infosecinstitute.com/topic/android-hacking-security-part-6-exploiting-debuggable-android-applications/
https://owasp.org/www-project-mobile-top-10/2016-risks/m3-insecure-communication


